Package arc.maps

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ImageLayer  
    MapGroupLayer
    Map layer containing a set of MapLayers, objects and properties
    MapLayer
    Map layer containing a set of objects and properties
    MapObject
    Generic Map entity with basic attributes like name, opacity, color
    MapProperties
    Set of string indexed values representing map elements' properties, allowing to retrieve, modify and add properties to the set.
    MapTile  
    TiledMap
    Represents a tiled map, adds the concept of tiles and tilesets.
    TileLayer
    Layer for a TiledMap
    TileLayer.Cell
    represents a cell in a TiledLayer: TiledMapTile, flip and rotation properties.
    TileSet
    Set of MapTile instances used to compose a TiledMapLayer
    TileSets
    Collection of TileSet
